Package ece325_lab_assignment4

Class Artist

java.lang.Object
ece325_lab_assignment4.Artist
All Implemented Interfaces:
ZooPerformer
public class Artist
extends java.lang.Object
implements ZooPerformer
Designed to be used with ZooShow class and will be in charge of:
  • Playing music and stopping music.
  • Keeping track of animal over feeding requests.
  • Call ZooAnimal.feed() to update animal feed tracking
Version:
1.10.0
Author:
corpaul, jeastgaa

      public void feed​(ZooAnimal animal) throws AlreadyFedException, NotPlayingException
      Feed the animal. Make sure to check whether we are allowed to feed this animal, and make sure to handle things correctly if we are not allowed to feed it. You are allowed to change this method's signature, if necessary.
      Specified by:
